  "slug": "angelosend",
  "title": "Angelo's End",
  "description": "A little update to The End, New Tools, Armor and more soon...",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/34de04ca72f8b090a151e1da7fcbc04e34809613.png\" />\n</div>\n\n<h2> </h2>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h3>Adds a new ore in The End!</h3>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ABetancourt03/angelosend\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2b46c0e322b5ff09b298c17cdfe6833c826ac74a.png\" />\n </a>\n\n <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/angelosend\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3494a91b8d02c32063e94ab08f6dd796b5bb4634.png\" />\n </a>\n\n <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/Q5Q71CX676\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4e525b7da08ae73392f08b3ef5da51ff72ef6889.png\" />\n </a>\n  \n  <div align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://fabricmc.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img width=\"191px\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b5f2bbe24d378d863f70c8b4bf7bf9c0ef2b56f7.png\" />\n </a>\n\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n     <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c4f1a960f18ab198a516e9e092572e3d4be63879.png\" />\n  </a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h2>Also works in Forge and NeoForge</h2>\n\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img width=\"300px\"  src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/538973c835bf323d8b0048512d61c0ff8aa30f0b.png\" />\n  </a>\n\n <div align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forgified-fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img  src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/167dc4a406313cb19c2e4bd1493d74180ab8c591.png\" />\n  </a>\n\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/connector-extras\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img  src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/81c4efc44654ac0db30652242292978d25f882b1.png\" />\n  </a>\n </div>\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h2>Ore Generation</h2>\n  <p>It generates between y20 and y35 at The End Islands.</p>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/b870d79dd7ad141b2220c0d7aa13867d74ef50d1.png\" />\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <h2>Recipes</h2>\n  \n  <h4>Enderite Scrap</h4>\n  <p>You can smelt Raw Enderite in a furnace or a blast furnace to get Enderite Scrap.</p>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/f6ecf4a5677554d3e1c5ce617b215f6beb73f13b.png\" />\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/4d3e7e0db101f8c02b7d2c504b680042a927c459.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Ingot Recipe</h4>\n  <p>You can get <strong>Enderite Ingot</strong> by combining 4 <strong>Enderite Scrap</strong>, 1 <strong>End Stone Block</strong>, 2 <strong>Chorus Flower</strong> and 2 <strong>Popped Chorus Fruit</strong> in the <strong>Crafting Table</strong>.</p>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/7e6d1ba631a4acfd8f32ebe9714e8516cfdca7f8.png\" />\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/66813b62a71ea06a35a63a24d4783064d75f2193.png\" />\n\n  <h2>Other Enderite Recipes</h2>\n\n  <h4>Block of Raw Enderite</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/0bd3cb7dd258d1edc8a9ff2f0f654817c33e4b04.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Raw Enderite from a Block of Raw Enderite</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/6770528ade3112439cb1b6d1b53acfca3afb1552.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Block of Enderite</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/6fe4e05be01a793b9e923ff3a60e2540cf0fdd90.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Ingot from a Block of Enderite</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/3e6e0b51b0df5261ca4167942f7427b37281c74c.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Upgrade Recipe</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/fe1bd108da8f9d78642040bcc96b0601f42841db.png\" />\n\n  <h2>Enderite Upgrade Generation</h2>\n  <p>You can find them at The End City chests.</p>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a3c9194546f6686d522b89c95608d9fd2982b790.png\" />\n\n  <h2>Upgrading Netherite Tools to Enderite</h2>\n\n  <h4>Enderite Sword</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/207cc875d9772a08388a364473ea7c0ae111776d.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Pickaxe</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/fd85bf7789ba65628dc59895fde24c2dc66801ad.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Axe</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/c3cc3b7f356bf566d6a83fe411c3ee8428b2a9bd.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Shovel</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/eebe583d0ea170d09c795a6491c0be5d3f1db15f.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Hoe</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/ed6c97706bea2777cc9ce8559e21c17adea1ed52.png\" />\n\n  <h2>Upgrading Netherite Armor to Enderite</h2>\n\n  <h4>Enderite Helmet</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/c3c2f62ebc642a809e5f30824d2ed822696ab122.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Chestplate</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/ba32d2cc9026e19bd56bfe2358e8a40ef74b1b0c.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Leggings</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/ebdfd8e931600591ace05ceedabed352994b0576.png\" />\n\n  <h4>Enderite Boots</h4>\n\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/bwbjkCOh/images/a6ce3b94da52d4456eb1b5ef1842fb6c2f77f53a.png\" />\n</div>",
